PLANTS OF SOUTH CAROLINA
HERBARIUM OF CLEMSON UNIVERSITY
CLEMSON, SOUTH CAROLINA

*Galax aphylla* L., Galax, Beetleweed, Skunkweed.

Diapensiaceae

Oconee Co.: Chau Ram County Park, on east side of Chauga
River and on south side of U.S. 76 about 2-1/4 miles from junction
of U.S. 76 with U.S. 123 in town of Westminster, S.C. Numerous
specimens present trailside in heavily wooded area.
